                    label.form__label(for='email') Email address
                    input#email.form__input.email_Signup(type='email', placeholder='you@example.com', required)
                    label.form__label(for='Name') Name
                    input#name.form__input.name_Signup(type='text', placeholder='eg. Utkarsh Raghuvanshi', required)
